<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ema613_04_IH_0006</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema613_04.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema613_04_ih_0006">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="6" class="is_star" lang="y">규민이는 우유 3.5 L를 일주일 동안 똑같이 나누어 마시려고 합니다. 하루에 마셔야 할 우유의 양은 몇 L인지 식을 쓰고 답을 구해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col mt_30">
          <div class="img_area">
            <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA613_04_IH/0006_01.png" alt="" />
          </div>
          <div class="input_area">
            <div class="flex gap_10 align_start">
              <span lang="y" class="label_gray">식</span>
              <div class="input_wrap input1">
                <math-field data-answer-single="3.5÷7"></math-field>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="input_wrap input2">
                <math-field data-answer-single="0.5"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap_10 align_start">
              <span lang="y" class="label_gray">답</span>
              <div class="input_wrap input2">
                <math-field data-answer-single="0.5"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p>일주일은 7일입니다.</p>
                <p>➔ (하루에 마셔야 할 우유의 양)</p>
                <p>=3.5÷7=0.5 (L)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
